description:
Lazy Boy is a character of a lazy gorilla boy named Dambo who lives in the African Jungles with his father, mother and a sister. They are a lazy family who rarely move but love to eat. 
Dambo's father’s name is Bingo, his mother is Abida and his sister is Alida.

They only occasionally hunt in the jungle to get meat food ingredients. Even though the family is lazy, they have hunting skills in their own way.

- Dambo is an archer 
- Bingo is a spear master
- Abida is a lasso expert
- Alida is a master of boomerang


Collectibles Plan =
#400 Dambo’s item characters
#400 Bingo’s item characters
